column2: SELECT u.up_name as [name], x.objID, str(p.ra,#,#) as ra,str(p.[dec],#,#) as dec, ISNULL(str(s.z,#,#),#) as Zsp, str(p.petroMag_r - p.extinction_r,#,#) as mpder_r, str(p.deVMag_r,#,#) as deVMag_r,str(p.deVRad_r,#,#) as deVRad_r, str(p.petroR5#_r,#,#) as petroR5#_r, str(p.petroR9#_r,#,#) as petroR9#_r, str(p.petroR9#_r / p.petroR5#_r,#,#) as C9#_r, dbo.fIAUFromEq(p.ra,p.[dec]) as SDSSname FROM  #x x, #upload u,  BESTDR8..PhotoObj as p LEFT OUTER JOIN BESTDR8..SpecObj s ON p.objID = s.bestObjID WHERE  ( p.type = # OR p.type = #) AND p.petroMag_r - p.extinction_r < # AND u.up_id = x.up_id AND x.objID=p.objID ORDER BY x.up_id
